text: Gianni Ryan Stensness (born 7 February 1999) is an Australian soccer player. He plays for Viking FK in the Eliteserien and for the Australia men's national soccer team (nicknamed the "Socceroos"). ==References== Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Australian men's soccer players Category:New Zealand footballers Category:Soccer players from Brisbane
